{"tid":838554,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩佬：Take Paul home","createTime":"2018-09-27T08:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:58:22.000Z","uid":4661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"424b7b7997748d77b534ba4c0b00d6f282e5e1a1","tid":838554,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180927/photo/bkn-20180927140508769-0927_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180927143619\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180927%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180927140508769-0927_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180927143619&h=64afd8f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外媒日前影到曼聯領隊莫連奴喺訓練場地同中場保羅普巴發生口角，各界都估緊，到底「寸王」當時同普巴講咗乜，搞到佢咁嬲呢。 <br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒指，莫連奴行過普巴身邊講咗句嘢，普巴回身問：「係咪講緊我？」莫帥回應：「Get Out(躝開)。」等同當眾炒普巴魷魚，對於呢位天價球星而言，實在係一大羞辱。 <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候保羅普巴立即黑面，跟住行前同「寸王」又拗咗幾句。有消息仲指，莫連奴跟住同人講：「Take Paul home(帶保羅普巴返歸)。」擺明要徹底鏟除呢位法國國腳。 <br />\n<br />\n英媒仲爆料話，當時莫連奴明知有電視台影緊，都去惹普巴，就係想激嬲佢，令佢發火做出魯莽事情，當眾出醜，咁就可以名正言順處罰佢，甚至出售佢。不過，普巴表現相對冷靜，令「寸王」奸計未得逞。"},{"pid":"57e5585d3a740006bcc4f9faca2c945a5f186cc4","tid":838554,"uid":4444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"好似之後叫左個助教問Pogba個ig story幾時post"},{"pid":"b68741c11586b589372966c9b882d846825d5632","tid":838554,"uid":302,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"摩佬：柒頭<br />\n普巴：係咪講緊我？<br />\n摩佬：帶佢去剪髮鋪"},{"pid":"075cc08d5e60cf8b4f9dce8616134c99f772c0a9","tid":838554,"uid":49702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"點睇得出佢黑面"},{"pid":"92d25341af4412edf2e3a79e9e37b19f2b7dc669","tid":838554,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4dc57f4bbf781a1b2493a5a5bb16d5d701a337d","tid":838554,"uid":46347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"以為叫史高斯番黎踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75099377d7a3ddc2055475e47cd3a76d5304dae","tid":838554,"uid":15993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4dc57f4bbf781a1b2493a5a5bb16d5d701a337d","tid":838554,"uid":46347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"以為叫史高斯番黎踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又出山"}]}